In the event of an emergency involving anhydrous ammonia, it is our policy to notify the Sigourney Fire Department and the Keokuk County LEPC and request that they respond to the emergency.  Our emergency action plans have been coordinated with both the fire department and LEPC.

7. Planned changes to improve safety. 

Safety improvement is an on-going process at the facility.  Periodic evaluations are performed to assess the maintenance of safe conditions.  There are no specific safety recommendations for implementation at this time.
